  <brief_title>Reverse Total Shoulder Arthroplasty Versus Open Reduction Internal Fixation of 3&amp;4 Part Proximal Humerus Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reverse Total Shoulder Arthroplasty Versus Open Reduction Internal Fixation of 3 &amp;Amp; 4-Part Proximal Humerus Fractures: A Randomized Prospective Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
